<div class="home-container">

  <!------------ navbar ------------>

  <%= render partial: "shared/navbar" %>

  <% flash.each do |type, msg| %>
    <div class="alert alert-info alert-dismissible fade in">
      <%= msg %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <!------------ banner ------------>

  <div class="home-banner">
    <div class="home-banner-box">
      <h1>KNOWLEDGE</h1>
      <h1>WISDOM</h1>
      <h1>EXPERIENCE</h1>
      <button class="btn home-button">DISCOVER</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!------------ profile ------------>

  <div class="home-profile">
    <div class="home-profile-box">
      <div class="home-profile-image-container">
        <div class="home-profile-image-border">
          <div class="home-profile-image">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="home-profile-content">
        <h5>LUCY BURNEY (FdSc, Dip ION) was the one of the first qualified nutritional therapist to specialize in children’s health and wellbeing in the uk.</h5>
        <p>Her three books, “Optimum Nutrition for Babies and Young Children”, “Superfoods for Healthy Kids”, and the highly successful, “Boost Your Child’s Immune System”, cover every growing stage of your child’s life from tot to teen.</p>
        <p>Published internationally, Lucy gained a reputation for her common sense approach to children’s health. Her books also make being a great parent as easy and straightforward as possible.  </p>
        <p>Lucy has frequently appeared on radio and TV, in newspapers and magazines and has contributed articles for magazines including The Tesco Baby Club and Natural Parent.</p>
        <p>Lucy arms parents with the tools to raise strong, healthy and happy children. This has never been more relevant and more important for a rewarding life in the modern world.</p>
        <p>READ ABOUT LUCY’S JOURNEY HERE</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!------------ recipes ------------>

  <div class="home-recipes">
    <div class="home-recipes-box">
      <div class="home-recipes-content">
        <h2 class="home-recipes-title">New Recipes</h2>
        <p>Enjoy lucy’s newest recipes, bursting with flavour, superfoods and nutrients to better support that healthy lifestyle we all aspire to have</p>
      </div>
      <div class="home-recipe-images">
        <div class="home-recipe-image r-img r-img-1"></div>
        <div class="home-recipe-image r-img r-img-2"></div>
        <div class="home-recipe-image r-img-3"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!------------ books ------------>

  <%= render partial: "shared/books" %>

  <!------------ newsletter ------------>

  <%= render partial: "shared/newsletter" %>

  <!------------ footer ------------>

  <%= render partial: "shared/footer" %>

</div>

